eville ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Sir Fulk Fitzwarin was born on 1 April 1389, in Coombe, Devon, England, United Kingdom, his father, Fulco IX Lord Fitz-Warin, was 28 and his mother, Lady Elizabeth Cogan, was 15. He had at least 1 son and 2 daughters with Lady Anne Botreaux. He died on 31 October 1407, in Wittington, Buckinghamshire, England, United Kingdom, at the age of 18."},"et":{"1 April 1389–31 October 1407":"1. aprill 1389–31. oktoober 1407","1389–1407":"1389–1407","1383–1420":"1383–1420","1404–1427":"1404–1427","1409–Female":"1409–Surnud","1419–1469":"1419–1469","1361–1391":"1361–1391","1374–1397":"1374–1397","31 October 1407":"31. oktoober 1407","8 August 1391":"8. august 1391","29 October 1397":"29. oktoober 1397","1374":"1374","1 April 1389":"1. aprill 1389","1361":"1361","1383":"1383","1391":"1391","1404":"1404","1469":"1469","1389":"1389","1420":"1420","1397":"1397","1409":"1409","1419":"1419","1407":"1407","1427":"1427","Combe Martin, Devon, England":"Combe Martin, Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Tawstock, Devon, England":"Tawstock, Devon, England","Coombe, Devon, England, United Kingdom":"Coombe, Devon, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Wittington, Buckinghamshire, England, United Kingdom":"Wittington, Buckinghamshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"1 April 1389–31 October 1407":"1. huhtikuuta 1389–31. lokakuuta 1407","1389–1407":"1389–1407","1383–1420":"1383–1420","1404–1427":"1404–1427","1409–Female":"1409–Kuollut","1419–1469":"1419–1469","1361–1391":"1361–1391","1374–1397":"1374–1397","31 October 1407":"31. lokakuuta 1407","8 August 1391":"8. elokuuta 1391","29 October 1397":"29. lokakuuta 1397","1374":"1374","1 April 1389":"1. huhtikuuta 1389","1361":"1361","1383":"1383","1391":"1391","1404":"1404","1469":"1469","1389":"1389","1420":"1420","1397":"1397","1409":"1409","1419":"1419","1407":"1407","1427":"1427","Combe Martin, Devon, England":"Combe Martin, Devon, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Tawstock, Devon, England":"Tawstock, Devon, Engla